Good Bye Tishaa: T-series Co-founder Krishan Kumar & Family, Bollywood Pay Last Respects To Their Daughter

In a heart-wrenching farewell, Krishan Kumar and family, along with the Bollywood fraternity, come together to pay their last respects to beloved Tishaa Kumar. Join us as we capture the emotional moments, heartfelt tributes, and the overwhelming support from friends, fans, and celebrities who gathered to honor Tishaa's memory. Watch as the industry bids goodbye to a shining star taken too soon.

'Bigg Boss OTT 3' Contestants Armaan Malik & Kritika Malik Spark Controversy with Leaked Alleged Intimate Video

Contestants Armaan Malik and Kritika Malik from 'Bigg Boss OTT 3' have found themselves in controversy due to a new video that shows them getting intimate under a blanket, which has sparked outrage among netizens. Some social media users are questioning the boundaries of reality shows after the clip was allegedly leaked from the show's 24/7 live feed and posted online. The intimate moment reportedly took place late at night while most housemates were asleep. Many viewers reacted strongly, trolling the couple for their actions.
